title: Local News: Comedian Teacher Wanjiku and husband Victor Ber welcome baby boy
text:
By May Jesaro Monday, Oct 12th 2015 at 08:08 
By May Jesaro ( @KiptuiMay ) 
Comedian Teacher Wanjiku and husband Victor Ber welcomed their first child yesterday, on Sunday evening. 
Their son Baby Zuri, came into this world receiving a warm welcome from family and friends. 
Teacher Wanjiku took it to her Facebook page, sharing the exciting news with her fans as she posted a picture of her baby. 
The couple got married in December 2014. 
SDE congratulates Mr and Mrs ber on their bundle of joy. SIMILAR STORIES
